Direct Known Subclasses:
GSTradComplexPrediction, LCMAComplexPrediction, OfflineComplexPrediction
public abstract class SPINComplexPrediction
extends Processor

This class handles the pipeline of complex prediction. It has to be specialized for each desired plain network based prediction algorithm.
